        levelID - the level ID
        inventory - the inventory for the level
        numberOfMechsToLose - number of mechs for that level to count as a loss for the player
        currentScore - current score on the level
        expectedSeconds - expected time to complete the level in seconds
        elapsedTime - elapsed time player spent on level in seconds
        mechs - list of mechs in level
        grid - the grid format of the level
        itemRespawnRate - the item respawn rate
